        "release_date": "1980-01-01T00:00:00.000Z",
        "description": "Step into the world of 10,000 BC with Stone Age, an immersive and interactive game designed for Virtual Reality. Explore the daily life of our ancient ancestors, understand how they interacted with their environment, and discover the tools and techniques they used to survive.\n\nStone Age offers a fascinating glimpse into the past, allowing you to experience the challenges and adventures of prehistoric life. Engage in various activities, from hunting and gathering to crafting and building, and learn about the ingenuity and resilience of early humans.\n\nFeatures:\n\n- **Historical Exploration:** Travel back to the Stone Age and explore the lifestyle of people from 10,000 BC.\n- **Ancient Tools:** Discover and use tools essential for survival in the Stone Age.\n- **Immersive Environment:** Experience a realistic and engaging prehistoric world with detailed graphics and sound effects.\n- **Educational Fun:** Learn about the history and culture of early humans in a fun and interactive way.\n\nDownload Stone Age and embark on an educational adventure that brings history to life through the power of virtual reality!",
